# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — Physics Debug Platform
# =============================================================================
# build/ 目录里包含：
#   - CMake 生成的项目文件（.sln / .vcxproj 等）
#   - 编译产物（.obj / .lib / .exe 等）
#   - FetchContent 自动下载并编译的第三方库：
#       build/_deps/joltphysics-src/   (JoltPhysics v5.3.0 源码)
#       build/_deps/joltphysics-build/ (JoltPhysics 编译产物，~266MB)
#       build/_deps/raylib-src/        (raylib 5.5 源码)
#       build/_deps/raylib-build/      (raylib 编译产物，~30MB)
#
# 第三方依赖无需放入仓库，clone 后执行以下命令即可自动还原：
#   cmake -B build -G "Visual Studio 17 2022"
#   cmake --build build --config Debug
# =============================================================================

# --- 构建目录（含所有编译产物和自动下载的依赖） ---
build/

# --- CMake 用户级缓存 ---
CMakeUserPresets.json

# --- 编译产物（万一在根目录有散落文件） ---
*.exe
*.obj
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.lib
*.dll

# --- Visual Studio ---
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.aps

# --- Windows ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- macOS ---
.DS_Store

# --- 编辑器临时文件 ---
*.swp
*.swo
*~
